Package: rnirs
Type: Package
Title: Chemometrics Methods and Locally Weighted Regressions
Version: 1.6-0
Author: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Maintainer: Matthieu Lesnoff <matthieu.lesnoff@cirad.fr>
Description: Package rnirs focuses on chemometrics methods, including locally weighted PLS regression and discrimination.The package is generic for any type of data, although it was initially implemented for near infrared spectral data (NIRS).
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Imports:  data.table, FNN, ggplot2, gridExtra, ptw, scales, signal 
Suggests: knitr, rmarkdown
URL: https://github.com/mlesnoff/rnirs
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: yes
